speaker: Jan Mulder (ALDE),
english: Jan Mulder (ALDE), rapporteur . – Mr President, I have just one additional question: is the Commissioner aware of the statement by a number of Member States in which they express their reservations about the agreement in the interinstitutional agreement that we concluded? What does he think the consequences of that statement will be and how will the Commission deal with that?
